# Everything a family generates at run time (`apm install` / `fit-benchmark
# run`), ignored once here so families don't each carry a copy. `apm install`
# also drops a per-family `.gitignore`; that generated noise is ignored too.
# `apm_modules/` and `node_modules/` are already covered by the repo-root
# .gitignore.
*/.claude/
*/apm.lock.yaml
*/.gitignore
*/bun.lock
